   with:\n-          inputs: requirements.txt requirements-dev.txt requirements-build.txt\n+          virtual-environment: .venv\n+          inputs: .\n+          locked: true\n \n       - name: <Deploy> Notify Discord of security testing result\n         uses: sarisia/actions-status-discord@v1\ndiff --git a/.github/workflows/test.yml b/.github/workflows/test.yml\nindex be6ee8ce7..9d5b19bef 100644\n--- a/.github/workflows/test.yml\n+++ b/.github/workflows/test.yml\n@@ -30,20 +30,6 @@ jobs:\n           uv lock\n           git diff --exit-code\n \n-      - name: <Test> Check dependency lists\n-        run: |\n-          uv export --no-annotate --no-hashes --no-header -o requirements.txt.check\n-          uv export --group dev --no-annotate --no-hashes --no-header -o requirements-dev.txt.check\n-          uv export --group build --no-annotate --no-hashes --no-header -o requirements-build.txt.check\n-\n-          diff -q requirements.txt requirements.txt.check || \\\n-          diff -q requirements-dev.txt requirements-dev.txt.check || \\\n-          diff -q requirements-build.txt requirements-build.txt.check > /dev/null\n-          if [ $? = 1 ]; then\n-            echo \"uv export has some diff\"\n-            exit 1\n-          fi\n-\n       - name: <Test> Check linting\n         run: uv run ruff check\n \n", "problem_statement": "`test-security`\u30ef\u30fc\u30af\u30d5\u30ed\u30fc\u306e\u5b9f\u884c\u81ea\u4f53\u304c\u5931\u6557\u3059\u308b\n## \u4e0d\u5177\u5408\u306e\u5185\u5bb9\n\n[`test-security`](https://github.com/VOICEVOX/voicevox_engine/actions/workflows/test-security.yml)\u30ef\u30fc\u30af\u30d5\u30ed\u30fc\u306e\u5b9f\u884c\u81ea\u4f53\u304c\u6700\u8fd1\u9023\u7d9a\u3067\u5931\u6557\u3057\u3066\u3044\u307e\u3059\u3002\n\n### \u73fe\u8c61\u30fb\u30ed\u30b0\n\n<details>\n\n<summary>test-security#21\u306e\u30ed\u30b0</summary>\n\n```log\n2026-01-15T04:38:11.7443978Z ##[group]Run pypa/gh-action-pip-audit@v1.1.0\n2026-01-15T04:38:11.7444300Z with:\n2026-01-15T04